verses.text_plain: O clap your hands, all ye people; shout unto God with the voice of triumph.
verses.verse_html:
1O clap your hands, all ye people; shout unto God with the voice of triumph. ▼
▼ for: or, of

verses.text_plain: For the Lord most high is terrible; he is a great King over all the earth.
verses.verse_html: 2For the Lord most high is terrible; he is a great King over all the earth.

verses.text_plain: He shall subdue the people under us, and the nations under our feet.
verses.verse_html: 3He shall subdue the people under us, and the nations under our feet.

verses.text_plain: He shall choose our inheritance for us, the excellency of Jacob whom he loved. Selah.
verses.verse_html: 4He shall choose our inheritance for us, the excellency of Jacob whom he loved. Selah.

verses.text_plain: God is gone up with a shout, the Lord with the sound of a trumpet.
verses.verse_html: 5God is gone up with a shout, the Lord with the sound of a trumpet.

verses.text_plain: Sing praises to God, sing praises: sing praises unto our King, sing praises.
verses.verse_html: 6Sing praises to God, sing praises: sing praises unto our King, sing praises.

verses.text_plain: For God is the King of all the earth: sing ye praises with understanding.
verses.verse_html:
7For God is the King of all the earth: sing ye praises with understanding. ▼
▼ with: or, every one that hath

footnotes.body_text: ▼ with: or, every one that hath
footnotes.body_html: ▼ with: or, every one that hath

verses.text_plain: God reigneth over the heathen: God sitteth upon the throne of his holiness.
verses.verse_html: 8God reigneth over the heathen: God sitteth upon the throne of his holiness.

verses.text_plain: The princes of the people are gathered together, even the people of the God of Abraham: for the shields of the earth belong unto God: he is greatly exalted.
verses.verse_html:
9The princes of the people are gathered together, even the people of the God of Abraham: for the shields of the earth belong unto God: he is greatly exalted. ▼
▼ princes…: or, voluntary of the people are gathered unto the people of the God of Abraham

footnotes.body_text: ▼ princes…: or, voluntary of the people are gathered unto the people of the God of Abraham
footnotes.body_html: ▼ princes…: or, voluntary of the people are gathered unto the people of the God of Abraham
